sections.heading: companies; rate regulations; violation; penalty
sections.text: Any person, firm or corporation, their employees, agents or servants, who shall violate any of the provisions of sections 70-407 and 70-408 shall be guilty of a Class V misdemeanor.SourceLaws 1933, c. 60, ยง 4, p. 292;C.S.Supp.,1941, ยง 70-508;R.S.1943,
